HEADWORD: Bishops-wort
<hw>Bish"op's-wort`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Wood betony (<spn>Stachys betonica</spn>); also, the plant called
fennel flower (<spn>Nigella Damascena</spn>), or
devil-in-a-bush.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bisie</ent>⟦br⟧
